Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:20.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.54,0:01:24.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そう言って彼女は　うつむいてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.26,0:01:30.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:38.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷たく張り付いて凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:45.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}降り続く現実に傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.53,0:01:52.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生きていく事が戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:56.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そんな理由だけで閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.11,0:01:59.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}マイハートマイストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.19,0:02:06.64,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:13.33,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ちいさな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空がうつる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:19.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ああ鳥のように飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:31.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰かを悲しませたとき感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:38.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れないように　そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:20.53,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若能让你忘却伤痛 我宁愿舍弃笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.54,0:01:24.25,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如是言语的她 默然低下了头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.26,0:01:30.98,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}任凭泪水洗刷着夜色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:38.76,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷漠蔓延着冻结一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.00,0:01:45.93,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仿佛这无可喘息的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.53,0:01:52.50,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生存就是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:56.10,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被这可悲的理由束缚着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.11,0:01:59.07,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My heart my story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.19,0:02:06.64,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪水的彼岸 那闪耀的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:13.33,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}狭小的窗口中 满眼是往昔的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:19.40,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然无法像鸟儿一样飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:31.57,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为让悲伤永远铭记于心而生的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:38.86,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为了忘却而闭目哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:15.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}花は風に揺れ踊るように　雨は大地を潤すように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:19.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}この世界は寄り添い合い　生きてるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:30.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}なぜ人は傷付け合うの　なぜ別れは訪れるの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:36.66,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}君が遠くに行ってもまだ　いつもこの心の真ん中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:40.98,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}あの優しい笑顔で埋め尽くされたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.13,0:21:50.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}抱きしめた君の欠片に　痛み感じてもまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:53.92,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}繋がるから　信じてるよ　また逢えると
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.92,0:21:55.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I am waiting for your love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:22:01.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you　I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:06.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}君の孤独を分けて欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:11.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you　I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:17.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}光でも闇でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:24.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}二人だから信じ合える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.72,0:22:30.01,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}NO 離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:15.09,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}如同花朵随风起舞 如同雨水滋润大地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:19.46,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}这个世界如此紧密不分 如此活泼生机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:30.96,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}却为何人们要互相伤害 为何离别会突然降临
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:36.66,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}即便去往遥远的地方 你总是会活在我心底
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:40.98,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}那份温柔的笑颜依旧映在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.13,0:21:50.14,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}拥抱着你的碎片 刺痛着我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:53.92,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}但心心相连 因为我坚信 会再见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.92,0:21:55.96,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I am waiting for your love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:22:01.23,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you  I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:06.63,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}多么想分担你的孤寂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:11.93,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you  I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:17.50,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}无论身处黑暗或是光明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:24.59,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}只要在一起就可以相信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.72,0:22:30.01,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}永远不再分离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.82,0:00:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要相互的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能将未来构筑起来!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗 露易丝!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺走那个未来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.22,0:00:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是天行者!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.94,0:00:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是战争的开始!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.97,0:00:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是世界的扭曲!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为沙慈的男人!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为你 准尉她!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢这样对中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特攻兵器!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.94,0:00:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再让你跑掉了 Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 露易丝你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.90,0:00:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是为了打倒你们的话!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚·爱德…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身为变革者…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:02:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了促使变革者出现而存在的人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原始变革体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要收回维塔了 里本斯·阿尔马克!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我说那个原始变革体进化了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我超越了原始变革体 成为了超越了真正变革者的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么大话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次不会射偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔掉武器投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会伤害你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了实现永久和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而最大的障碍就是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要接受变革者的支配吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被优秀的存在所统治
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在伦理角度上也是正确的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 为了引导人类而诞生的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不会向我们索取任何回报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是理想的关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就会失去自由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全的自由是对道德的摒弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方有的只是毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在秩序的社会中 人们会满足于被限定的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被关在笼子中保护的人也会感到舒适
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打着根除战争的旗号 实际上却在扰乱世界的人 就是你们!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在将世界委托于变革者 才能带来真正的永久和平
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么就不明白呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明人类长久以来追求的理想乡就要实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来如果不是由我们自己开创的话 就没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:05:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去的罪孽 如果不亲手了却的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不会迎来真正的未来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…我会战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难缠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天什么者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.47,0:05:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子剩余量!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 沙慈·库洛斯洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 露易丝呢?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带她到安全的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知…知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是超越变革者的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维塔不会给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 引导人类的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝 露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝 露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧 死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易…丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙… 慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝 怎么了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是纯正的变革者的力量?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登鼻子上脸!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕林克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发动TRANS-AM攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了 露易丝!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝 露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}露易丝 沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了以自身的意识创造未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.29,0:09:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你 就不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.52,0:09:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷鲁亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.26,0:09:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 托勒密就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹的残量!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩 琳达
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家生命正在消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混账
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生的!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个GN粒子!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这光不是战争之物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个光辉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份光芒 肯定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那战斗的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是生命的闪烁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:10:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变吧 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替没能改变的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.65,0:11:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了创造未来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…要改变!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑…脑量子波被扰乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那个Gundam的话 我们就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里杰诺·瑞婕塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯正的变革者的脑量子波和TWIN DRIVE联动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯度提升的GN粒子将放大人类的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于完全进化了吗 刹那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是真正的变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.51,0:11:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么? 这种恶心的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这畜牲…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥他们就是因为你这种混账才!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈! 你小子原来是那个男人的弟弟啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是又怎么样了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有杀的价值了啊～!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你他妈的算什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子就是老子!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰了你!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刹那吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别给我管别的 阿雷鲁亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷鲁亚!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛只对着玛丽就行了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种不可思议的现象是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑内 竟然会直接响起声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 比利…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明知道明白的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却还一味地任性…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口… 不是那样的!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 为了恒久和平的实现才…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是决定了为了那个才战斗的!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一直喜欢你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷鲁亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 安德雷少尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是声音!? 皮瑞斯中尉么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就算继续憎恨你 最终能够报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐也一定不会开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴! 你这个叛徒!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么 要把血肉之亲的大佐给…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人也背叛了军队!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是他应得的报应!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他扰乱了恒久和平!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐不是会那么做的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.15,0:14:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对! 那家伙是看着妈妈死去了的人!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能相信他!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 没有试着相互理解呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人什么都没有对我说!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借口也好! 谢罪也好!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心情他根本就没有理会!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我杀了他!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己亲手!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己也是也想要被理解的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.91,0:14:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有去试着理解大佐呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐他一定 是有在想着你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么为什么那时候什么都不跟我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不跟我说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:15:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是什么都不知道吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不跟我说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机80%击落!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放松啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对的!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了? 身体的疼痛被…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不用说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 这份好温暖的光芒是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像心都要溶进去一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刹那哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是他内心的光芒…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是照亮未来的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维塔的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红哈罗 机体交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.86,0:16:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.81,0:16:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,… 刚才的GN粒子是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的脑量子波给扰乱…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算等到这个时候了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:16:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里杰诺·瑞婕塔!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维塔拒绝了和我的链接!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道把系统给…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里本斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你为所欲为的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧? 提艾利亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Se… Seraphim
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,审判领域正在生成的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:41.46,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(762,1008)}TRIALFIELD
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和维塔链接的机体 都渐渐停下来了的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维塔的支援竟然!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的提艾利亚·爱德!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经夺回来了呢 维塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 战斗就能结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于动用那个了么 提艾利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧? 玛丽!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 阿雷鲁亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎… 怎么了发生了什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈的 快给老子动啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没资格说老哥什么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这家伙 不能饶恕!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑啊 你他妈的!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙把老爸 老妈 还有艾美…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连老哥也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们 真心相爱的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心相爱的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽 多亏了有你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在觉得 人与人相互理解的世界也不是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 就算被世界所排斥也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要接受惩罚也好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会战斗下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为天行者的Gundam机师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是 维塔的本体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚·爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定为你报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随便就把人说成死人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里 提艾利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我的意识 完全和维塔链接着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维塔?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.38,0:20:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为变革者…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 原始变革体觉得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为用这份能力能救助了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:20:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过和维塔的链接
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了所有的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.42,0:21:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚计划的全貌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.72,0:22:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 我现在暂时返航
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.95,0:22:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.47,0:22:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚计划…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.20,0:22:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的武力介入行动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.60,0:22:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了促进不断孕生矛盾的世界进行统合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.39,0:22:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算毁灭它
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要达成人类意志的统一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.71,0:22:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:22:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防止人类抱着战争的火种
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:22:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就向着外宇宙进发
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类 不改变的话就无法通向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是为了 有朝一日同相遇的异种族间的对话…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.46,0:23:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此 我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.86,0:23:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要相互理解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.76,0:23:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seraphim 破损严重!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚呢!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.48,0:23:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有反应…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.65,0:23:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再好好找啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.39,0:23:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.56,0:23:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在审判领域之中 还有能动的敌人?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.95,0:23:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.30,0:23:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越了变革者的变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.74,0:23:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里本斯·阿尔马克!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.81,0:23:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你记得感谢我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.25,0:23:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能得到那份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.61,0:23:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是多亏了我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.18,0:23:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里本斯·阿尔马克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.84,0:24:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.77,0:24:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成变革的同类赌上未来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.69,0:24:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展开了最后的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.92,0:24:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.62,0:24:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新时代的序幕 在此拉起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:53.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)\fs35\a7}I love you　I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:58.54,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)\fs35\a7}君の孤独を分けて欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:03.74,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)\fs35\a7}I love you　I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:09.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)\fs35\a7}光でも闇でも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:16.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)\fs35\a7}二人だから信じ合える
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:22.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)\fs35\a7}NO 離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:58.54,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)\fs45\a7}多么想分担你的孤寂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:09.03,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)\fs45\a7}无论身处黑暗或是光明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:16.46,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)\fs45\a7}只要在一起就可以相信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:22.23,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)\fs45\a7}永远不再分离


